#: templates/pages/about.html:8
msgid "À propos de PLAGENOR"
msgstr "About PLAGENOR"

#: templates/pages/about.html:15
msgid ""
"L'ESSBO (École Supérieure en Sciences Biologiques d'Oran) héberge PLAGENOR, "
"un service commun de recherche financé par la DGRSDT (Direction Générale de "
"la Recherche Scientifique et du Développement Technologique)."
msgstr "ESSBO (Higher School of Biological Sciences of Oran) hosts PLAGENOR, a shared research facility funded by DGRSDT (General Directorate of Scientific Research and Technological Development)."

#: templates/pages/about.html:18
msgid ""
"PLAGENOR héberge GENOCLAB, la filiale commerciale (SPA) de l'ESSBO, régie "
"par le code de commerce algérien."
msgstr "PLAGENOR hosts GENOCLAB, the commercial subsidiary (SPA) of ESSBO, governed by Algerian commercial law."

#: templates/pages/about.html:21
msgid ""
"PLAGENOR 4.0 est la plateforme numérique de gestion de toutes les activités "
"de PLAGENOR — agissant comme un ERP interne pour organiser les flux de "
"travail, gérer les demandes IBTIKAR et les clients GENOCLAB."
msgstr "PLAGENOR 4.0 is the digital management platform for all PLAGENOR activities — acting as an internal ERP to organize workflows, manage IBTIKAR requests and GENOCLAB clients."

#: templates/pages/about.html:28
msgid "Deux missions"
msgstr "Two Missions"

#: templates/pages/about.html:30
msgid ""
"Canal académique : réaliser des analyses génomiques pour les étudiants de "
"fin de cycle (Master, Ingéniorat) et les doctorants de toutes les "
"universités algériennes, afin de promouvoir la recherche scientifique en "
"Algérie. Chaque étudiant éligible dispose d'un budget annuel virtuel de 200 "
"000 DA géré par la DGRSDT."
msgstr "Academic channel: perform genomic analyses for final-year students (Master, Engineering) and doctoral students from all Algerian universities, to promote scientific research in Algeria. Each eligible student has a virtual annual budget of 200,000 DZD managed by DGRSDT."

#: templates/pages/about.html:33
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Canal commercial : fournir les mêmes analyses génomiques aux clients "
"externes (entreprises, hôpitaux, laboratoires privés, particuliers) sur une "
"base commerciale avec facturation, TVA 19%%%%, et paiement réel."
msgstr "Commercial channel: provide the same genomic analyses to external clients (companies, hospitals, private laboratories, individuals) on a commercial basis with invoicing, 19%% VAT, and real payment."

#: templates/pages/about.html:42
msgid ""
"Identification microbienne (MALDI-TOF), séquençage Sanger & Illumina, PCR, "
"contrôle qualité des acides nucléiques, lyophilisation, synthèse d'amorces."
msgstr "Microbial identification (MALDI-TOF), Sanger & Illumina sequencing, PCR, nucleic acid quality control, lyophilization, primer synthesis."

